    "body" : "<p>I don't know if this is resolved for you, but it took me a long time to figure it out too. What I did:</p>\n\n<p>First I created a launch.json file using the Java plugin.<br>\nThen I edited the <code>mainClass</code> variable to <code>myfilename.java</code>. I had the same error as you if I only put <code>myfilename</code> in the <code>mainClass</code> variable.</p>\n\n<p>As last step you need to modify <code>classPath</code> to include whatever .jar you need for the project.</p>\n"
